'''Zinedine Zidane''' (23 Kamena 1972, izina mu [[cyarabu]]: زين الدين يزيد زيدان) ni umukinnyi w'umufaransa wagacishijeho m'umupira w'amaguru, wakinaga nka nomero ya 10 mu kibuga mu ikipe y'igihugu y'ubufaransa akaba yarakoze amateka mu makipe nka: [[AS Cannes|Cannes]], [[FC Girondins de Bordeaux|Bordeaux]], [[Juventus F.C.|Juventus]] na Real Madrid yaje kubera umutoza ndetse akayayifasha gutwara ibikombe bikomeye harimo n'icya UEFA  akaza kwegura  ku wa kane 31 ,Gicurasi ,2018 .<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/amakuru-53441096</ref><ref>https://igihe.com/imikino/football/article/zinedine-zidane-yeguye-ku-butoza-bwa-real-madrid?url_reload=31</ref> <ref>https://rushyashya.net/bitunguranye-zinedine-zidane-yeguye-ku-mirimo-yo-gutoza-real-madrid/</ref>.

Yatowe nk'umukinnyi mwiza ku mugabane w'uburayi na [[UEFA Golden Jubilee Poll]]. yakinnye umukino wa mbere mu ikipe y'igihugu taliki ya 17 kanama 1994, mu mukino wa gicuti wahuzaga [[Ubufaransa]] na  [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic]] aho yinjiye mu kibuga asimbura agafasha ikipe ye kunganya ibitego 2-2 nyuma yo gutsinda ibitego bibire wenyine.

